different users are going to

00:17:32.640 --> 00:17:35.360
interpret it in different
ways.

00:17:35.360 --> 00:17:37.430
And so, logout totally
makes sense.

00:17:37.430 --> 00:17:38.910
Disconnect me from
your services.

00:17:38.910 --> 00:17:40.340
I don't want to get
any more messages.

00:17:40.340 --> 00:17:41.550
100% makes sense.

00:17:41.550 --> 00:17:42.700
Exit--

00:17:42.700 --> 00:17:43.550
it doesn't.

00:17:43.550 --> 00:17:45.662
Basically what you're describing
what the Exit

00:17:45.662 --> 00:17:48.160
button does, it sounds to me
like what should happen when I

00:17:48.160 --> 00:17:52.690
hit Back or Home from
within your app

00:17:52.690 --> 00:17:53.500
AUDIENCE: That's what
